The '''Acme Anvil''' is the company's flagship product and the original entry in the [[ACME Inc|ACME]] catalogue. Available since 2006, it set the design standards that later product lines were built around.

The Anvil remains the highest-volume item in ACME's range and is supported and developed by the [[ACME Engineering|engineering team]] based at the [[ACME Amsterdam HQ|Amsterdam headquarters]].
